data.description: This is a great opportunity to enjoy country living where you can have chickens, a garden, open space to enjoy and what an great view to the east while sitting on your deck. This ranch plan features an open floor plan from the living room to the eatin kitchen. From the eating area you can access the deck that stretches all along the back side giving you an unobstructed view to the east, which is beautiful. The spacious primary bedroom has a walk in closet and private access to a full bath plus, an added bonus is access to the deck. Main floor laundry room is a real treat, no going up and down stairs to do laundry.  Located on just over an acre of land. The red 32' shed to the east stays, the red shed to the west (front) does not stay. This is truly a rare opportunity to own an acreage in the country under $500k.  Very easy to show.
